    "result": {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Zeyu's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"8a88f3e8-ac93-5dcd-9302-813163e8e2e3","excerpt":"一个多月没更新了，开学以后总是有各种各样的琐事。不过好在大四确实没什么过重的课程，主要还是把重心给放在毕业设计上。这一个月和 Amin 聊天，聊着聊着就决定要把 Music 和 Image 结合起来，做一个 novel 的 work 出来。主要还是因为，纯 AI Composer 想要发 paper…","html":"<p>一个多月没更新了，开学以后总是有各种各样的琐事。不过好在大四确实没什么过重的课程，主要还是把重心给放在毕业设计上。这一个月和 Amin 聊天，聊着聊着就决定要把 Music 和 Image 结合起来，做一个 novel 的 work 出来。主要还是因为，纯 AI Composer 想要发 paper 还是比较困难的，很多 work 的复杂程度还是不在我的能力范围之内。而凭借一些三脚猫的 CV 知识，就打算把 CNN based 图像处理和 RNN based 自然语言处理（symbolic data of music）结合一下，搞点能 publish 的 work！</p>\n<h2>Intro &#x26; Motivation</h2>\n<p>先来看一下这篇 paper 在干什么吧：图像风格迁移。下图中的钢铁侠，是 content image；梵高的画《星空》，是 style image，最终生成了“星空”风格的钢铁侠。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/cd138/1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.32911392405063%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/f058b/1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/c26ae/1.png 158w,\n/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/6bdcf/1.png 315w,\n/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/f058b/1.png 630w,\n/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/40601/1.png 945w,\n/static/f4e356941df2f6cd77f8965a74e1f90e/cd138/1.png 1220w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>其实风格迁移，本质上是一个 Texture (纹理) transfer problem，在现有方法中，大多都只能实现 low-level 的图像特征提取，对于不同风格的语义化提取还是比较困难的。这篇 paper 的主要贡献就在：把语义提取变成了神经网络中损失函数的最优化问题。</p>\n<h2>Encoding: Deep Image Representation</h2>\n<h3>Content Representation</h3>\n<p>F（对于生成图像）和 P（对于原始图像）代表 Content 的内容。假设在 layer l 中有 N 个 filters，M 代表每个 filter 的尺寸（长*宽），那么 F 和 P 就是 一个 N * M 维的矩阵，F 的下标 i，j 代表在 layer l 中 第 i 个 filter 在 j 这个位置的 activation。例如一张 RGB 图像，为 3*255*255，那么代表有 3 个 filters 和 255*255 的尺寸。Content Loss 函数及其导数表示如下：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/be86f/2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 22.78481012658228%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"2\"\n        src=\"/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/f058b/2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/c26ae/2.png 158w,\n/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/6bdcf/2.png 315w,\n/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/f058b/2.png 630w,\n/static/74aa515a12ca42ccda754020a5490495/be86f/2.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/be86f/3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.417721518987342%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"3\"\n        src=\"/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/f058b/3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/c26ae/3.png 158w,\n/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/6bdcf/3.png 315w,\n/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/f058b/3.png 630w,\n/static/cd8afe921ffbeb979d23113bcbe34412/be86f/3.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Style Representation</h3>\n<p>G（对于生成图像）和 A（对于样式图像）代表 style 的内容。G 的下标 i，j 代表：在 layer l 中， filter i 和 filter j 在相同位置下 activation 的乘积之和（遍历所有位置）。E 则代表了类似 Style Loss 函数的子项（对每一层 layer 而言，N 与 M 对应 content representation 中的定义，在这里作为归一化的参数）。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/31493/4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 43.0379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"4\"\n        title=\"4\"\n        src=\"/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/f058b/4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/c26ae/4.png 158w,\n/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/6bdcf/4.png 315w,\n/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/f058b/4.png 630w,\n/static/63fe673a1d8f4ef9a2fa9bbd241fb2bd/31493/4.png 664w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/31493/5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.316455696202528%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"5\"\n        src=\"/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/f058b/5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/c26ae/5.png 158w,\n/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/6bdcf/5.png 315w,\n/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/f058b/5.png 630w,\n/static/212f7da05b43ccebad2f1c08b7b7955e/31493/5.png 664w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>同样，style loss 函数 (w 用来决定每一层的权重) 以及其导数被定义如下：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/be86f/6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.405063291139236%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"6\"\n        title=\"6\"\n        src=\"/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/f058b/6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/c26ae/6.png 158w,\n/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/6bdcf/6.png 315w,\n/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/f058b/6.png 630w,\n/static/1c47d6da49eb0c2cab5f1e55712d9494/be86f/6.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/be86f/7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.354430379746837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"7\"\n        title=\"7\"\n        src=\"/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/f058b/7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/c26ae/7.png 158w,\n/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/6bdcf/7.png 315w,\n/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/f058b/7.png 630w,\n/static/09bdd2c40cc9793b6a0af76ffd94f455/be86f/7.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Style Transfer Algorithm</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/133ae/8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.69620253164557%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"8\"\n        title=\"8\"\n        src=\"/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/f058b/8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/c26ae/8.png 158w,\n/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/6bdcf/8.png 315w,\n/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/f058b/8.png 630w,\n/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/40601/8.png 945w,\n/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/78612/8.png 1260w,\n/static/24d4f3f6f4cc8b8ecc910e5557a1f623/133ae/8.png 1424w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这里就到了算法的核心部分，左图代表 style image，右图代表 content image，中间这张图是 generated image。我们可以观察到，从 content image 的卷积层中，随机抽取一层，将它的 content 与 generated image 进行 loss 计算。而 generated image 与 style image 的每一层都存在 loss 计算。根据它们的导数，我们进行 back propagation 来调整梯度下降的学习率。我们的最终目标，是要把 total loss（公式如下，是 style loss 和 content loss 的线性组合）降低到最小。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/b79a5/9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.025316455696203%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAZElEQVQI1zVORwoEMQyb/38zpBKn4BSYw2iRYQ8CYTU/IvKOMaCqn/ceKSXDOQe1VuP3Xqy1jNMz50RrDc4500opCCFARPCo6htjpPHjsfduwt7bQjlnK6JGcISFfOI/TjDD+w+k1ZZwqQ9wogAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"9\"\n        title=\"9\"\n        src=\"/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/f058b/9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/c26ae/9.png 158w,\n/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/6bdcf/9.png 315w,\n/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/f058b/9.png 630w,\n/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/40601/9.png 945w,\n/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/78612/9.png 1260w,\n/static/d22eeb2d612c73c4232affbb80d403b0/b79a5/9.png 1372w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Result</h2>\n<p>接下来，让我们来看看结果：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/2e694/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.0506329113924%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/f058b/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/c26ae/10.png 158w,\n/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/6bdcf/10.png 315w,\n/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/f058b/10.png 630w,\n/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/40601/10.png 945w,\n/static/fcdf7728281db31b9c411c49b47c7659/2e694/10.png 1048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A 是原图（content image），B 的风格源于特纳的画《米诺陶战舰的倾覆》，C 的风格源于梵高的画《星空》，D 的风格源于蒙克的画《Der Schrei》。</p>\n<p>在参数方面，a/b 的值：B 为 0.001，C 为 0.0008，D 为 0.005。这三张图都是从原图的 <code class=\"language-text\">conv4_2</code> 这一层 match 的 content loss，而在 style loss 方面，<code class=\"language-text\">conv1_1</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">conv2_1</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">conv3_1</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">conv4_1</code>，<code class=\"language-text\">conv5_1</code> 的权重 w 被设置为 0.2，其他层被设置为 0。</p>\n<h2>Discussion</h2>\n<p>在这里我们主要讨论影响生成图像质量的因素。</p>\n<h3>Trade-off between content and style matching</h3>\n<p>a/b 的值会影响图像的表达，这个值越小，越偏向 style image，反之越偏向 content image。还记得之前的 A 图吗，我们依然把它作为 content image，将下图作为 style image：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 312px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2887cf6436828abd70a9538609a7ac5e/17474/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11\"\n        title=\"11\"\n        src=\"/static/2887cf6436828abd70a9538609a7ac5e/17474/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2887cf6436828abd70a9538609a7ac5e/c26ae/11.png 158w,\n/static/2887cf6436828abd70a9538609a7ac5e/17474/11.png 312w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 312px) 100vw, 312px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>下面是在不同的 a/b 比值下的结果（结论应该一目了然）：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/27b7a/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.64556962025317%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"12\"\n        title=\"12\"\n        src=\"/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/f058b/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/c26ae/12.png 158w,\n/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/6bdcf/12.png 315w,\n/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/f058b/12.png 630w,\n/static/3c32555b4c882b71a1088163760e41fd/27b7a/12.png 804w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Effect of different layers of CNN</h3>\n<p>实验证明，在 high layers 来 match content loss 所生成的图像更加平滑。例如我们将下图作为 content image:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 574px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/882b1c22d504fffbcc1d199a380baf3d/86389/13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.30379746835443%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"13\"\n        title=\"13\"\n        src=\"/static/882b1c22d504fffbcc1d199a380baf3d/86389/13.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/882b1c22d504fffbcc1d199a380baf3d/c26ae/13.png 158w,\n/static/882b1c22d504fffbcc1d199a380baf3d/6bdcf/13.png 315w,\n/static/882b1c22d504fffbcc1d199a380baf3d/86389/13.png 574w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>在不同 layer 进行 match 所得到的结果（<code class=\"language-text\">conv2_2</code>为 low layer，<code class=\"language-text\">conv4_2</code>为 high layer）：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/30d16/14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.74683544303798%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"14\"\n        title=\"14\"\n        src=\"/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/f058b/14.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/c26ae/14.png 158w,\n/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/6bdcf/14.png 315w,\n/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/f058b/14.png 630w,\n/static/afb7d3aa2af336f3c361de29f41686c5/30d16/14.png 672w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Initialization of gradient descent</h3>\n<p>生成图像最开始的样子应该是 content image？style image？还是某些有白噪声的 image？</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/374ac/15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.177215189873415%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"15\"\n        title=\"15\"\n        src=\"/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/f058b/15.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/c26ae/15.png 158w,\n/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/6bdcf/15.png 315w,\n/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/f058b/15.png 630w,\n/static/acdf374051c2a2ee4e323b6a3cd07746/374ac/15.png 634w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 612px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5916cd4831b127626301020cb74a361d/8c76f/16.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.88607594936708%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"16\"\n        title=\"16\"\n        src=\"/static/5916cd4831b127626301020cb74a361d/8c76f/16.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5916cd4831b127626301020cb74a361d/c26ae/16.png 158w,\n/static/5916cd4831b127626301020cb74a361d/6bdcf/16.png 315w,\n/static/5916cd4831b127626301020cb74a361d/8c76f/16.png 612w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>A 为初始化为 content image 的最终结果。</p>\n<p>B 为初始化为 style image 的最终结果。</p>\n<p>C 为初始化为 white noise image 的最终结果。</p>\n<h3>Photorealistic style transfer</h3>\n<p>如果 style image 不是抽象画，而是一张真实的照片，怎么办？我们的算法依然可以做到：例如下面展示的，content image 是白天的伦敦，style image 是夜晚的纽约，最后生成夜晚的伦敦。即使生成的图像没那么真实，但整体色彩和内容还是很到位的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/587b0/17.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.87341772151898%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"17\"\n        title=\"17\"\n        src=\"/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/f058b/17.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/c26ae/17.png 158w,\n/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/6bdcf/17.png 315w,\n/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/f058b/17.png 630w,\n/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/40601/17.png 945w,\n/static/361da433957b96f018130e452eec27c0/587b0/17.png 970w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>My Thought</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>第一眼看到图像风格迁移，我以为是手动标记一些 label，然后在神经网络中去 predict 某张图片属于什么 label 并与之匹配，融合。结果没想到不需要手动标记 label，完全是在直接进行两张图片的融合。这对于数据收集耗时问题是一个很大的帮助。</li>\n<li>关于 evaluation 的问题，因为艺术创作本来就没有标准答案，属于这块可以做得比较模糊。萝卜青菜各有所爱，大不了做一些 investigation 来当作 evaluation 也未尝不可。</li>\n<li>可以试着换一个神经网络结构去重新做实验，看看效果是否会更加明显。关于各种参数影响生成图像风格的讨论，还可以分得更细。例如，对于风格是抽象画的作品，什么 a/b 的比值和 activation layer 会比较好，反之，对于现实主义的画作，甚至是拍摄作品，怎样的参数又会更加合适。</li>\n<li>给 FYP 的启示：核心算法还是一个 loss optimization 的问题，主要是要研究一下 music encoding 和 image encoding 中有哪些共性可以转换。</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"Image Style Transfer Using Convolutional Neural Networks","date":"October 16, 2021","description":"Final Year Project 相关论文：图像风格迁移 CVPR 2016"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Programming/react-native-ip-camera-tensorflow/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React Native: IP Camera LiveStream Prediction"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Life/River/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The River"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"8a88f3e8-ac93-5dcd-9302-813163e8e2e3","previousPostId":"eea0b30f-91cd-5c7e-8a15-0ce5d1671634","nextPostId":"b1767888-d131-5b90-a1ea-3627fde9ca70"}},
